  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>The Purchase Order (PO) List View page provides a list of orders created within the last 90 days. If you are searching for older POs or other specific details, the queue can be filtered by status, date created, and other fields. From the List View page, you can also create new POs, view and edit POs to reconcile them, and import POs.</p><h3 id=\"PurchaseOrders:ListView-AdditionalResources\">Additional Resources</h3><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932427416/Purchase+Order+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932427416\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Order Resources</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932722231/Purchase+Order+Process+Creating+a+New+Purchase+Order\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932722231\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Order Process: Creating a New Purchase Order</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932787800/Purchase+Order+Process+Receiving+Items+and+Reconciling+the+Order\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932787800\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Order Process: Receiving Items and Reconciling the Order</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1931411625/Purchase+Orders+Importing+and+Uploading\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1931411625\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Orders: Importing and Uploading</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932394561/Purchase+Orders+Exporting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932394561\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Purchase Orders: Exporting</a></p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/Technical%20-%20124a6d.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"PurchaseOrders:ListView-ViewingandNavigatingthePurchaseOrderListViewPage\">Viewing and Navigating the Purchase Order List View Page</h2><p /><p>On the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Inventory</strong> \u2192 <strong>Purchase</strong> <strong>Orders</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"564\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%201.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>The Purchase Order List View is sorted by PO identification (ID) number on the left column. Columns can also be sorted by clicking on the header of the column you would like to sort.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%202.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>You can use filters to see POs by Supplier, Location, Status, and Keyword Search by ID number.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"680\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%203.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: After applying your filters, click the <strong>Apply</strong> button to see the results. To clear filters, click the <strong>Reset</strong> button.</p><p /><p>You can save <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1932754986/List+Views\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1932754986\" data-linked-resource-version=\"12\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">filters as default views</a> and customize what columns of information are displayed by clicking the<strong> Options (\u22ee) button</strong> near the top right of the page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>You can start a new Purchase Order by clicking the <strong>Add (+) button</strong> near the top right of the page, next to the <strong>Options (\u22ee) button</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%205.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>You can view available actions for a purchase order next to the line item. Under the Actions column, click the <strong>Options (\u22ee) button</strong> next to the purchase order for options to View, Edit, or Print the PO.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%204.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>You can import a PO by clicking the <strong>Options (\u22ee) button</strong> and selecting <strong>Import</strong>. A new import field will appear below your Purchase Order list.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1932787831/PO%20List%20View%206.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p><strong>Note</strong>: Imported Purchase Orders must be imported as a tab-delimited text file. To download a template with proper formatting for uploading, click <strong>Purchase Order Import Template</strong>. For more help importing data into RepairQ, check out <a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1931411625/Purchase+Orders+Importing+and+Uploading\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1931411625\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Importing Purchase Orders</a>.</p><p /><p /><p>START 1.18.X</p>",
